text: San Lorenzo is a corregimiento in San Lorenzo District, Chiriquí Province, Panama. It has a land area of and had a population of 2,290 as of 2010, giving it a population density of . Its population as of 1990 was 1,621; its population as of 2000 was 1,772. ==References== Category:Corregimientos of Chiriquí Province
